This branch is up to date with `merge-TeX-fixing`.  

### major changes in 
- [play.ts](/two-ticks/p5.teach.js/blob/merge-TeX/src/lib/Scene/play.ts)
- [TeX.ts](/two-ticks/p5.teach.js/blob/merge-TeX/src/lib/MObject/TeX.ts)
- [tex.test.ts](/two-ticks/p5.teach.js/blob/merge-TeX/src/test/MObject/tex.test.ts)

### to-do
- [x] documentation
- [x] animations fixed
- [x] camelCase syntax
- [x] modular `play` function
- [x] typescript interfaces
- [x] test cases
